                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>character. If you are determined<lb/> to misconstrue our words we<lb/> cannot help\n                it.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Trusting that our relations<lb/> will assume a more harmonious<lb/>\n                aspect We remain</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(10)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">A. S. Cohen &amp; Co</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p>P. S. The members of the firm are<lb/>\n                <persName role=\"author\">A. S. Cohen</persName> of the N. Y. Evening Express<lb/> and\n                    <persName>Mr. L. Israel</persName> (well known<lb/> to you.)</p>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>"
                  },
